comment:
Australian Whiskey always cops a bit of flack for being more expensive but in this case, it’s well worth it

Tiger Snake is a brilliant take on the bourbon style of whisky and the vanilla soaked almond note is phenomenal.
Easy to drink neat or with a dash of water (if you must) but is also a great mixer for that special evening with friends.

5 stars, my favourite whiskey!

This is not bad but I just can't justify the price with so many top whiskies in the price range. This is sweet and clean and that's as good as it gets 

Dan Murphy whisky tasting 13 sept 17
Did nothing for me. Winning plenty over but yeah nah. Just wasn't my thing. Will have to give another go at some point to double check
